</head>

<style>

div{

    width:300px;
    padding:30px;
    border:5px solid rgb(10, 63, 10);
    margin:20px;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    background-color:rgb(222, 222, 168);
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div>

demonstration of CSS Box Model.

</div>

</body>
</html>



